{"tid":1992520,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Apink普美「視訊簽售」突淚崩　粉絲一聽原因⋯也哭了！","createTime":"2020-04-28T07:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T08:46:01.000Z","uid":74065,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"13bece03ac284349c59634fca4dc3be3bf082692","tid":1992520,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:51:30.000Z","msg":"南韓女團「Apink」於2011年出道，至今已有9年，成員們各個長相甜美、能歌善舞，在綜藝節目上也總是不計形象搞笑，沒有偶像包袱的模樣更是圈了大批粉絲，近日不僅帶著新作品回歸，也舉辦了「視訊簽售」與歌迷互動，怎料普美卻在通話途中落淚，原因公開後藏著滿滿的洋蔥，更讓不少網友心揪了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4844/d4844615.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4844%2Fd4844615.jpg&h=c559f2ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲Apink這次回歸成績相當亮眼。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\nApink在4月13日發行第九張迷你專輯《LOOK》，一同慶祝出道9週年，其中主打歌《Dumhdurum》公開後，便獲得廣大的迴響，在僅僅5個小時內就獲得各大音源排行榜的第一名，登上音樂節目後，甚至連續6天獲得音樂放送的冠軍，繳出漂亮的成績單。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4844/d4844619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4844%2Fd4844619.jpg&h=92f6e7a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲普美「視訊簽售」到一半突然哭了。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，Apink除了努力在音樂節目上打歌之外，也舉辦了「視訊簽售」與歌迷見面，因為新冠肺炎疫情延燒，只能選擇透過手機來互動。然而，有一名日本粉絲便在推特分享了一段與普美視訊的內容，只見他不斷地秀出以前的海報給普美看，看著看著普美就突然紅了眼眶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4844/d4844617.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4844%2Fd4844617.jpg&h=877cf597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲普美「視訊簽售」到一半突然哭了。（圖／翻攝自推特／manabun46）<br />\n<br />\n原來是，普美有一位來自日本的粉絲過世了，那一位與她視訊的歌迷在通話的過程中，努力地想要將朋友的愛傳達給她，對方慢慢地道出「他（過世的粉絲）說謝謝普美給他一段這麼美好的時光」、「這些海報都是他的寶物」等，感動的話語讓普美忍不住在鏡頭前淚崩，也讓許多網友爆哭，紛紛留言「感受到普美的真心，粉絲與偶像的愛是雙向的」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/manabun46/status/1254723471537344513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanabun46%2Fstatus%2F1254723471537344513&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=889a0630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanabun46%2Fstatus%2F1254723471537344513&h=b0a3934e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/manabun46/status/1254723471537344513</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/manabun46/status/1254748869906198528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanabun46%2Fstatus%2F1254748869906198528&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPqCH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=fde00c1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanabun46%2Fstatus%2F1254748869906198528&h=5e6d7e48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/manabun46/status/1254748869906198528</a><br />\n<br />\n吊...睇到我都咸左...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754edb71cb95cfa26e259822a4ad52a918f137f5","tid":1992520,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"扮嘢到"},{"pid":"6446878c83af7fa60ce2c121306efbb5f958a8e7","tid":1992520,"uid":235316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:53:20.000Z","msg":"[行動po]香港人日程表更新<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1992311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1992311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"073786ece2b8e344086237a5e4e3d20eafd103aa","tid":1992520,"uid":80047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"754edb71cb95cfa26e259822a4ad52a918f137f5","tid":1992520,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"扮嘢到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T07:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c9857322fe03d0e8ce73db630e03a9898f0b45","tid":1992520,"uid":256952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"073786ece2b8e344086237a5e4e3d20eafd103aa","tid":1992520,"uid"